Then: 1 + 2 = 3 = 2M - 18 => 2M = 21 => M = 10.5, which is not an integer. So, invalid. Next, try a = 1, b = 3: 1 + 3 = 4 = 2M - 18 => 2M = 22 => M = 11. Let's check if this works. M = 11. Then, a =
